title: transfer data from iphone ios14 (beta) to google pixel 4XL
content:
Has anyone had trouble transferring / setting up iPhone XS that has ios14 beta to a google pixel?
it just skips right over the transfer data and goes to google account backup instead (which doesnt copy over everything), and sometimes shows an error if you click back

i'm thinking this is because i have ios14 beta OP on my iPhone is why its not working, but i cant restore my iPhone without loosing data... 

anyone had a similar issue and found a way around this?
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 4 XL
